IN RE: Ken DOHRE NO. 2018-B-0941 Supreme Court of Louisiana. October 29, 2018

ATTORNEY DISCIPLINARY PROCEEDING

PER CURIAM

The Office of Disciplinary Counsel seeks review of an order of the disciplinary board that the formal charges against respondent, Ken Dohre, be dismissed. Having reviewed the record and the briefs of the parties and amici curiae, we find the disciplinary board reached the correct result in dismissing the formal charges.

Accordingly, it is the judgment of this court that the formal charges against respondent be dismissed.

FORMAL CHARGES DISMISSED.

Hughes, J., dissents.
